com.realestate.ui

Class SearchResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.support.v4.app.Fragment
      • com.realestate.custom.CustomFragment
        • com.realestate.ui.SearchResult
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.view.View.OnClickListener, android.view.View.OnCreateContextMenuListener

    public class SearchResult
extends CustomFragment
    The Class SearchResult is the Fragment class that is launched when the user clicks on Search option Search screen and it simply shows a dummy list of Search results with a MapView that shows dummy locations for properties. You can customize this to load and display actual search result listing.
